| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3751 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5217db37-73fa-5ff9-8f1c-9028a4ba8333"
